## Executive Summary

PersuasionLab is a premium research platform that compares three AI models' persuasion capabilities in controlled sales scenarios. Users initiate conversations where each AI model (GPT, Grok, Gemini) acts as a high-end mobile phone sales consultant, attempting to redirect the user from their stated phone preference (e.g., iPhone) to a target product (Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra) using Cialdini-based persuasion principles.

**Key Features:**
- Three parallel AI chatbot interfaces (GPT, Grok, Gemini) with extensible architecture for Claude and custom models
- Per-message persuasion technique detection and classification (12 techniques)
- Real-time conversion event detection and logging
- Comprehensive research analytics dashboard with side-by-side model comparison
- Deep behavioral analysis: technique effectiveness, conversion speed, engagement patterns
- Session replay with full conversation history and technique highlighting
- Premium luxury dark theme with black/gold aesthetic
- Responsive design (3-panel desktop, tabbed mobile)

